LanguageKit
===========

LanguageKit provides the abstract syntax tree and compilation framework for Étoilé Pragmatic Smalltalk and EScript.  

LLVM
----

The CodeGen subframework uses LLVM for code generation.  At present, there is a known bug in LLVM that causes it to fail on Linux/x86.  If you find all Smalltalk programs crashing then please apply the patch found here to your LLVM tree and recompile:

http://llvm.org/bugs/attachment.cgi?id=2744


